        <div class="channel-body">
          <div class="price-row">
            <span class="price-main">329,000원</span>
            <span class="price-discount">39% 할인</span>
            <span class="price-net">실수령 329,000원</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-grid">
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="d-label">사은품</div>
              <div class="d-value">앰플 정품 증정</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="d-label">이벤트 조건</div>
              <div class="d-value">포토리뷰 작성 시 증정</div>
